Hi @jhseu, don't care about my last comment.
So, I just run

`bazel build tensorflow/tools/api/tests:api_compatibility_test`
`bazel-bin/tensorflow/tools/api/tests/api_compatibility_test --update_goldens True`
as described in the README and it says

s.s.
----------------------------------------------------------------------
Ran 4 tests in 0.001s

OK (skipped=2)

But there are in fact no changed files I could commmit. I am little puzzled with this part. Do you have some advice?
